{"tid":730480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20歲以下全職收入中位數5年增1000元　政府：明顯上升","createTime":"2018-07-05T12:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T15:24:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6b572b4fc023b944cc516c2671933952528d7335","tid":730480,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180704/s00001/ee4bd688daa12148c19626b994393a29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180704%2Fs00001%2Fee4bd688daa12148c19626b994393a29.jpg&h=9fec4e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港年輕一代的入息水平和上流機會，近年更受關注。政務司長張建宗今日書面回覆工聯會立法會議員陸頌雄提問時指出，本港20歲以下全職工作人士的每月實質收入中位數，在過去5年增加1000元；20至29歲人士則增加1600元。政府引述數據時表示，「各年齡組別的全職僱員每月就業收入中位數在期內均明顯上升」，年輕畢業生的工資有顯著增長。<br />\n<br />\n政府援引統計處綜合住戶統計的調查顯示，2013至2017年各年齡層的每月就業收入中位數（不包括外籍家庭傭工），當中反映50至59歲人士的實質就業收入中位數變化最多，增加2500元至1.8萬元；其次為增加1800元至1.3萬的60至69歲階層。<br />\n<br />\n針對年輕人階層，20以下人士由9200元升至去年1.02萬元，僅有1000元的增長；20至29歲人士則由1.34萬元升至1.5萬元，增加1600元。<br />\n<br />\n對此，政府回應指，「數據顯示，各年齡組別的全職僱員每月就業收入中位數在期內均明顯上升」，形容隨着經濟發展，近年年輕畢業生的工資有顯著增長，現屆政府將繼續為青年人締造上流機會。<br />\n<br />\n2013年和2017年各年齡層全職僱員的每月就業收入中位數（2013年/2017年）：<br />\n<br />\n20歲以下 （9200元/10,200元）<br />\n<br />\n20至29歲 （13,400元/15,000元）<br />\n<br />\n30至39歲 （18,400元/20,000元）<br />\n<br />\n40至49歲 （19,000元/20,000元）<br />\n<br />\n50至59歲 （15,500元/18,000元）<br />\n<br />\n60至69歲 （11,200元/13,000元）<br />\n<br />\n70歲及以上（10,100元/10,000元）<br />\n<br />\n註：不包括外籍家庭傭工<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180704/s00001/1530696908195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180704%2Fs00001%2F1530696908195&d=wz%2FZjKwIRaCioXb8dQfv8dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e206c016\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180704%2Fs00001%2F1530696908195&h=4f62aa87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180704/s00001/1530696908195</a>"},{"pid":"88e769648e6da162aa25fba4d93da33f38259d17","tid":730480,"uid":79793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:31:58.000Z","msg":"連登標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b89bc46c235da5f0fe66eb29bf7edcd8472b32","tid":730480,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:32:45.000Z","msg":"連登仔出黎統計下"},{"pid":"a6dbd4f3e45b080c3d3e120b23f752c2ad0c209b","tid":730480,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0b89bc46c235da5f0fe66eb29bf7edcd8472b32","tid":730480,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:32:45.000Z","msg":"連登仔出黎統計下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:39:50.000Z","msg":"月入60k"},{"pid":"c5cce5998a8c23ea5ae9be05b33b0c3cbc4f793d","tid":730480,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:41:08.000Z","msg":"我由5500蚊升到7500蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n升幅達到35% <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7c74219f478261cd5aff19e8c3b29eed17aed7","tid":730480,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:41:58.000Z","msg":"原來我既價值同一個退休人士差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a5368c20166e27e2f586c7dff8c6b628f96d5c","tid":730480,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"我想問如果拎呢抽數據做標準 一個普通人靠自己要幾耐先買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd1005802845eee75ddd1d261e1e8baea0f78b5","tid":730480,"uid":38528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:44:03.000Z","msg":"以為一年升左1千,原來5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl